data.description: BACK ON MARKET THRU NO FAULT OF SELLER! 1.6 Acres with Garage. Hiking the Appalachian Trails, or your own property even, skipping over to the Winery, tubing in Helen, restaurants, shops, and being able to return to your very own Log Home Retreat with every tree or bush you could imagine, including bananas! Possessing over 2000 sq. ft., Floor to Ceiling gas fireplace, and with each floor having its own private bed and bath, a chef's kitchen with center island and a place to display all those cooks' pots and pans, additionally with a view of your parkland. If that wasn't enough you have tongue and groove in immaculate hardwood floors, Hi Speed Internet, and your very own storm shelter. This is the dream cabin you have been waiting for. Sellers thought was to install a gate and fence to make it an even more private retreat, but due to medical circumstances must move ASAP.
